<p>In Engine Room episode #6, David Gray, CEO of FedUp Foods, joins us to share his insights from investing in food production businesses and also managing Food &amp; Beverage businesses (Greenseed Contract Packaging and FedUp Foods). Specifically, we dive into the latest trends in Food &amp; Bev, the most pressing challenges, and best advice for other F&amp;B companies who are trying to navigate both in this tough economic time.</p> <p>The episode is available on <a href="https://youtu.be/ARvcrsJBFys?si=Si-rTZR3iWeaUn2g">YouTube</a>, <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/episode-6-food-beverage-manufacturing-with-david-gray/id1709724213?i=1000634692226">Apple Podcast app</a>, and <a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/4aSaSwkEZu4Xe5sR3gLAta?si=7HpY2bpYSbK0WA2jFz-okQ">Spotify</a>. Enjoy!</p>
